---
title: "US08 — Log out"
---
sequenceDiagram
  actor A as Registered Free User
  participant B as «Boundary»<br/>ProfileScreen
  participant C as «Control»<br/>Authenticate
  participant E as «Entity»<br/>Profile
  A->>B: tap LOG OUT
  B->>C: signOut()
  C->>E: end session, clear cached Profile
  E-->>C: session cleared
  C-->>B: auth state = signed out
  B-->>A: redirect to Login
  note over E: via AuthGateway → Supabase Auth
